{"tid":630716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無意撤出敘利亞 美國將向俄羅斯實施新一輪制裁","createTime":"2018-04-15T23:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T17:41:57.000Z","uid":147314,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"41c6789541a438a36813d129690314d59c6ce4a7","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:48:54.000Z","msg":"黑利稱美國將就敘利亞懷疑使用化武向俄國實施新制裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1391326_2_L_20180416061521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1391326_2_L_20180416061521.jpg&h=19e59123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑利稱美國將向俄羅斯實施新一輪制裁。（美聯社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國駐聯合國大使黑利表示，美國本星期將就敘利亞懷疑使用化武襲擊，向俄羅斯實施新制裁。<br />\n<br />\n黑利接受美國傳媒訪問時說，財政部最快星期一公布，制裁將針對協助敘利亞政府製造及運送化武的俄羅斯公司。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，美軍無意撤出敘利亞，除非擊敗「伊斯蘭國」武裝分子，確保敘利亞不使用化武，以及保持對伊朗監視的能力。<br />\n<br />\n黑利表明，美國不會同敘利亞總統巴沙爾單對單會談。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391326-20180416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391326-20180416.htm&d=O%2Bj7jUNsDTeIMO4choCzP%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=e93b8623\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391326-20180416.htm&h=2c41a38d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391326-20180416.htm</a>"},{"pid":"827a600b48d6dd6d99290c76fa81c3892a760132","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:50:32.000Z","msg":"美英法就敘利亞問題向安理會提新決議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1391334_1_L_20180416035236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1391334_1_L_20180416035236.jpg&h=27bdee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三國擬就敘利亞問題提出新決議（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n美英法聯合空襲敘利亞化武設施後，三國周六向聯合國安理會提出新決議。<br />\n<br />\n據法新社取得的決議文件顯示，三國要求調查杜馬鎮的化武襲擊，人道主義救援物資能夠暢通無阻地進入敘利亞，又要求敘利亞參與由聯合國主導的和談。<br />\n<br />\n另外，周六抵達大馬士革的國際禁止化武組織代表，在酒店與敘利亞外交官員會面，暫時未知他們何時前往杜馬鎮調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391334-20180416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391334-20180416.htm&d=O%2Bj7jUNsDTeIMO4choCzP%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=0ece2a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391334-20180416.htm&h=172f85ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391334-20180416.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f80faa65561bf8b5de6d995f6fbefce7f47ca94a","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:51:56.000Z","msg":"彭斯稱華府準備好再次打擊敘利亞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1391289_1_L_20180415162325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1391289_1_L_20180415162325.jpg&h=e0dd9868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭斯在秘魯表示，美國準備好再次打擊敘利亞。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯表示，華府已經準備好再次軍事打擊敘利亞，並且應對敘利亞可能採取的報復行動。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯在秘魯出席美洲國家首腦會議，他向傳媒表示，美英法的聯合行動，打擊了敘利亞發動化武攻擊的能力。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯表示，敘利亞巴沙爾政府如果再次使用化學武器，將要付出極大代價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391289-20180415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391289-20180415.htm&d=O%2Bj7jUNsDTeIMO4choCzP%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=a8204f7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391289-20180415.htm&h=a12bd26c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391289-20180415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"78471771f57e3cd92e55c35f51ed287863d6551f","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"敘利亞衝突：美擴大對俄製裁 中國緊跟俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/5008/production/_100888402_046179821-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F5008%2Fproduction%2F_100888402_046179821-1.jpg&h=d06b2971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周六凌晨，英國皇家空軍的一架狂風戰鬥機攜帶兩枚「風暴之影」巡航導彈，正凖備開始對敘利亞目標的攻擊。AFP<br />\n<br />\n美英法聯軍攻擊敘利亞化武設施，使西方與俄羅斯之間的矛盾更趨激化。俄羅斯試圖在聯合國譴責聯軍行動，但只獲得中國和玻利維亞支持。美國則凖備加強對俄製裁。<br />\n<br />\n由於敘利亞城市杜馬發生疑似毒氣攻擊，美國聯合英國和法國於周六（4月14日）凌晨對敘利亞軍事設施實施了精凖打擊。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普說，一旦敘利亞再次使用化學武器，美國將再次對其發動攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京則警告西方，如果再次攻擊敘利亞，將在國際上導致&quot;混亂&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n在西方與俄羅斯之間，中國政府採取了堅定支持俄羅斯的立場，不僅在官方媒體大肆批評西方，還在聯合國安理會支持俄羅斯譴責美英法的議案。"},{"pid":"bcab33b4cea7bedf1acd4e5c41bc979dff7c2ede","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:56:34.000Z","msg":"特朗普：美國已&quot;子彈上膛&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/6FAC/production/_100888582_5db9cf2e-d5a4-4be2-b103-1139b8d570d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F6FAC%2Fproduction%2F_100888582_5db9cf2e-d5a4-4be2-b103-1139b8d570d3.jpg&h=fca1256e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄羅斯試圖推動聯合國安理會譴責聯軍行動，但未成功。圖為美國和英國代表投票反對俄羅斯的決議草案。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周六在推特上說，美國、英國和法國&quot;完美地執行&quot;了針對敘利亞的軍事打擊。特朗普感謝英法盟友，並說這次襲擊已經&quot;大功告成&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n同日，美國駐聯合國代表尼基&middot;黑利在聯合國引述特朗普的話說：&quot;如果敘利亞政權再次使用毒氣，美國已將子彈上膛。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n黑利說：&quot;我們的總統一旦劃下紅線，他就會堅守這條紅線。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人桑德斯周日對美國廣播公司（ABC）說，特朗普總統在敘利亞的長期目標是&mdash;&mdash;擊敗&quot;伊斯蘭國&quot;組織，遏制伊朗的野心，並制止化學武器的使用。<br />\n<br />\n黑利周日接受美國哥倫比亞廣播公司採訪時說，由於俄羅斯繼續支持敘利亞阿薩德政權，美國將於周一宣佈擴大對俄羅斯的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n她說，美國的新一輪制裁措施將直接針對向阿薩德政府提供化武設施和其他裝備的俄羅斯公司。"},{"pid":"19ef1d0b649aa68826fd3ca7b68720af82d6483e","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:57:36.000Z","msg":"普京：攻擊敘利亞將導致&quot;混亂&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/13A68/production/_100888408_046107869-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F13A68%2Fproduction%2F_100888408_046107869-1.jpg&h=6a8ab89f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普京警告西方，再次攻擊敘利亞將導致「混亂」。REUTERS<br />\n<br />\n聯軍攻擊敘利亞後，俄羅斯繼續堅定支持阿薩德政權，普京總統還對聯軍的行動予以&quot;最強烈的譴責&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n周日，普京與伊朗總統魯哈尼通了電話。伊朗和俄羅斯一樣，也派兵參與敘利亞內戰，支持阿薩德政權。<br />\n<br />\n普京對魯哈尼說，如果西方再次攻擊敘利亞，&quot;將不可避免地導致國際關係中的混亂&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n耐人尋味的是，就在普京上述談話發表前，俄羅斯外交部副部長裏亞布科夫（Sergey Ryabkov）釋放出較為緩和的信號。<br />\n<br />\n裏亞布科夫對塔斯社說，俄羅斯將利用一切機會緩解目前&quot;極端危險&quot;的政治局勢。"},{"pid":"418a13567be02b91535c3cd130644d14a7262b73","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:58:51.000Z","msg":"俄譴責聯軍行動 僅三票支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/96BC/production/_100888583_5dab3e93-c6f6-4347-9a77-f27f664a8d47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F96BC%2Fproduction%2F_100888583_5dab3e93-c6f6-4347-9a77-f27f664a8d47.jpg&h=79c52863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國在安理會投票支持俄羅斯譴責聯軍行動的決議草案。除中俄兩國外，只有玻利維亞投了贊成票。GETTY IMAGES<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯表面上很強硬，但由於前雙面諜在英國中毒事件以及敘利亞化武攻擊事件，該國在國際上已日趨孤立。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯周六在聯合國安理會召集緊急會議，試圖推動安理會通過決議，譴責聯軍對敘利亞的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n但是，俄羅斯的決議草案僅獲得安理會15個成員國中的三票支持，因此被否決。除了俄羅斯自己，僅有中國和玻利維亞投了贊成票。<br />\n<br />\n除了在聯合國緊跟俄羅斯，中國政府還通過官方媒體批評美英法的軍事行動。<br />\n<br />\n中共黨報《人民日報》周日發表評論文章，批評西方的&quot;任性軍事干預害處多多&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》子報《環球時報》則發表社評說，&quot;美英法對敘實施任性攻擊是可恥的&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43778620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43778620&d=O%2Bj7jUNsDTeIMO4choCzP%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=54123b31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43778620&h=4a8c3588\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43778620</a>"},{"pid":"e7b62e4f5ae6c14cf0c862f79155aeac18d06766","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d3ea464f78fb9cfa96261bea7546648be45dee","tid":630716,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b0bec5ec2cecb6c7d699595d2e38680adb87e45","tid":630716,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那"},{"pid":"f87b45d802c5a4c45bb207bab86046bae493eae7","tid":630716,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:28:52.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅世界第二大經濟體有咩作為?<br />\n<br />\n老解咁強大，點解唔打鳩美帝、解放敘利亞人民?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五毛唔出聲嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被Tomahawk 炸撚死矖呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d12ae3e3e04ad12c515960a0f5ce947d50c9a5","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:32:40.000Z","msg":"2017年 6月 21日<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-40359838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-40359838&d=O%2Bj7jUNsDTeIMO4choCzP%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=19acc505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-40359838&h=77dbd04e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-40359838</a><br />\n<br />\n布朗克認為，S-400能夠關閉敘利亞和塞浦路斯領空，因此構成了明顯的長期威脅。不過分析家也認為，在敘利亞使用S-400也會給俄羅斯帶來巨大風險。<br />\n<br />\n布朗克說：&quot;如果俄羅斯使用了S-400但不奏效，那就是個打擊，因為俄羅斯依賴S-400保衛加裏寧格勒和俄羅斯本土&quot;，&quot;在那個地區美國及其盟友有如此多的海空力量，對俄羅斯來說前景很不妙。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f383e3477785dd22891de703250e0708f8b849","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975044070ee5e428536c133a8d7131cde60c33d5","tid":630716,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"點解唔係用&quot;克莉&quot;?"},{"pid":"ee2da9f997d3a1e45c80d0bf947d39e819c6ffe5","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"975044070ee5e428536c133a8d7131cde60c33d5","tid":630716,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"點解唔係用&quot;克莉&quot;?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66f87a22e9e7a9694b5600d48ef32aadee84d10","tid":630716,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"幾正 想屌"},{"pid":"e5dd1ea457d821e0498b2c74f1a9d925ae896346","tid":630716,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"到左呢個時候, 中共仲要跟住俄佬, 係唔係唔識死??"},{"pid":"0cee750ed6545603b9721b3906e0b473316ed3f5","tid":630716,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}